      • MapsRepository

        @Inject
public MapsRepository(UsersRepository usersRepository,
                               CitiesRepository citiesRepository)
        Constructs the basis of any DTORepository. Initializes the BeanRepository.bean's property and the BeanRepository.superBean with the passed dto as well as initializes BeanRepository.beansList. Constructor calls setupInitialBean(M) and startInternalInitialization().

      • requestMapsOfCity

        public void requestMapsOfCity()
        This method sends the server a request to fetch all the maps that are attached to the currently selected city in CitiesRepository. In addition, it will fetch all available maps, i.e., NOT attached to any city. See ClientsInquiry.Inquiry.MAP_OF_CITY_FETCH_ALL.
